item.title: FAQ
item.description: About the beta version Is FireDucks beta available for free? Yes Can I use FireDucks beta for commercial purposes? Yes Is FireDucks beta OSS? No About the release to manufacturing (RTM) version When will the RTM version of FireDucks be released? Not determined yet What will the license be applied for the RTM version of FireDucks? Not determined yet About support Is there support for FireDucks? As far as we know, no organization offers paid support for FireDucks.
